      "text": "Review Role  →  spawnRun(issueId, 'review', { subRole: 'security' })\n                         ↓\n              resolveModel('review', 'security')  ←  config.yaml  roles.review.sub.security.model  (workhorse refs resolve here)\n                         ↓\n              generateLauncherScript(harness, resolvedModel)  →  tmux session per reviewer  (full agent, own env, own cost tracking)",
